name: TARDIGENERATE 02/10
description:
Inspired by the tardigrade, this interactive generative piece, created with p5.js, features a creature that moves around the canvas and interacts with the mouse (or tap on mobile). 

Move the mouse into the canvas to set a target for the creature, which will follow the target around. Move the mouse off of the canvas to remove the target, leaving the creature to wander on its own.

This is object 2 of a series of 10.
